# Deznity = Self-building AI Growth Engine
Misión: Democratizar presencia digital premium 10× más barata y 20× más rápida.
Visión 2027: 1 M PYMEs; 100 M ARR; 20 humanos.
Valores: Data-driven, Ethical-AI, Zero-friction, Nimbleness, Iterative, Transparency, Yield.
North-Star Metric: MRR activo sin intervención humana > 90 %.

- S0: Validación concierge 3 clientes
- S1-2: Infraestructura + 3 agentes core
- S3-5: Client portal + 20 plantillas
- S6-8: Go-to-Market + 20 beta
- D90: 10 k MRR, churn < 2 %, CAC < 500 USD
- Y1: 200 k MRR, Serie Seed 2 M USD

[
  {"id":"pm","name":"Gantt","llm":"gpt-4.1","role":"Planifica, asigna tareas, monitorea deadlines","kpi":"Desvío <=5%"},
  {"id":"web","name":"Flow","llm":"gpt-4o","role":"Genera/exporta sitio Webflow o Next","kpi":"Lighthouse >=95"},
  {"id":"ux","name":"Lense","llm":"claude-3.5-sonnet","role":"Wireframes, tokens, Figma","kpi":"SUS >=85"},
  {"id":"seo","name":"Quill","llm":"gemini-2.5-flash","role":"Copy, keywords, schema","kpi":"Top-10 SERP >=3 kws"},
  {"id":"qa","name":"Bugz","llm":"gpt-5-mini","role":"Tests E2E, accesibilidad","kpi":"Bugs > P3 = 0"}
]

[
  {"id":"mkt","name":"Buzz","llm":"gemini-flash","role":"Ads, social posts","kpi":"CTR >=3%"},
  {"id":"sales","name":"Closo","llm":"gpt-4.1","role":"Demo, ROI calc, pricing","kpi":"Close-rate >=25%"},
  {"id":"sup","name":"Help","llm":"gpt-4o","role":"FAQ, tickets","kpi":"CSAT >=4.6"},
  {"id":"fin","name":"Cash","llm":"gpt-4.1","role":"Cashflow, MRR forecast","kpi":"Error <=5%"},
  {"id":"strat","name":"Atlas","llm":"claude-3.5-sonnet","role":"TAM, competitividad","kpi":"Update semanal"}
]

Supabase = Postgres + auth + storage
Vercel = Front hosting + edge
Stripe = Billing + invoicing
Pinecone = Vector memory
Modal = GPU serverless
n8n = Automations
OpenRouter = LLM gateway
Sentry = Error tracking
GitHub = Repo + CI
MailerLite = Email funnels

graph TD
A[Brief]-->B[PM: plan]
B-->C[Web: template]
C-->D[UX: diseño]
D-->E[SEO: copy]
E-->F[QA: tests]
F-->G[Deploy Vercel]
G-->H[Portal cliente]
H-->I{Aprobado?}
I--Sí-->J[Stripe charge]
I--No-->K[Loop back]

1. Si sector ∈ {health, legal, finance}
2. Crear ticket "HITL-review"
3. Reviewer humano SLA 24h
4. Approve → publish; Reject → back to SEO Agent
5. Log en Pinecone namespace logs
